          cta: 'Une dernière chance · 147 EUR',
          gif: 'https://media.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExeHY3Y21hZHpub3Nva2djM2J0emtuZTgzcGx2NnI1bTcwZTg5MTd2cyZlcD12MV9naWZzX3NlYXJjaCZjdD1n/Rmil7OaM9xcAg/giphy.gif'
        },
        {
